en.name: Magpul Masada 5.56x45 assault rifle
en.description: The Masada is a much rarer instance of the popular Remington ACR, which was designed as a next-generation modular rifle intended to blend the best features of several proven platforms. Built around a fully ambidextrous, user-configurable architecture, the rifle allows for quick caliber changes through barrel-swaps. Manufactured by Magpul.

Built around a fully ambidextrous, user-configurable architecture, the rifle allows for quick caliber changes through barrel-swaps. Manufactured by Magpul. Flat Dark Earth version.

en.name: Magpul Masada 5.56x45 assault rifle (Custom)
en.description: The Masada is a much rarer instance of the popular Remington ACR, which was designed as a next-generation modular rifle intended to blend the best features of several proven platforms. Built around a fully ambidextrous, user-configurable architecture, the rifle allows for quick caliber changes through barrel-swaps. Manufactured by Magpul. This version has been adapted to use the .300 Blackout Cartridge.
